cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM

This paper deals with the use of deep learning techniques for image analysis, specifically for counting mitosis in breast cancer images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms and the processing of large amounts of image data, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The authors also mention the use of image segmentation techniques, which could be relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
